videos.headline: Doaks cuts outside for the Cincy TD
videos.description: Gerrid Doaks wins the race outside and scores the 10-yard touchdown to put Cincinnati on the board first.

videos.headline: Whyle climbs the ladder for a Cincinnati TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder tosses the fade to Josh Whyle, who outleaps his defender for the 13-yard Cincinnati touchdown.
